OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAnother bright day with some
OL,6,Fsunshine at times and becoming hot
OL,7,Faway from immediate coasts. Later
OL,8,Fthere is a slight chance of the odd
OL,9,Fheavy shower and becoming somewhat
OL,10,Fcloudier.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FDry at first with some
OL,13,Fbrightness, but increasingly cloudy
OL,14,Fthrough the evening and overnight.
OL,15,FMostly dry but some light drizzle
OL,16,Fpossible and perhaps the odd heavier
OL,17,Fshower in the north.
OL,18,
OL,19,CSaturday:FAny heavier showers soon
OL,20,Fclearing in the morning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
