OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fstart on Sunday then brightening up
OL,7,Fwith sunny intervals. Monday and
OL,8,FTuesday dry with sunny spells and
OL,9,Fbecoming warmer inland, cooler along
OL,10,Fimmediate coasts.
